<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>动物们试图阻止毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他已经向村庄跑去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黄昏时分，他到了草地。他害怕极了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都很早就从田里回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们没在准备晚饭，而是聚在无花果树下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们生气地大喊着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利悄悄地向麦苏雅的小屋走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他偷偷地透过窗户往里面看，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只见麦苏雅的丈夫被绑在床上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦苏雅躺在地上，嘴被堵着，手脚被绑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她吃力地喘着气，痛苦地呻吟着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利吓了一跳。麦苏雅被打得很严重。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利很了解村民们的习惯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只要人们能吃饭和聊天，他们就会待在树下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但当布尔迪奥没抓到毛克利回到村庄时，他们就会回来的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利从窗户溜进了小屋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他弯腰切断了麦苏雅和她丈夫身上的绳子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦苏雅看起来十分痛苦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利用手捂住她的嘴，免得她尖叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你会来的。”麦苏雅抽泣着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你是我的儿子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是谁干的？”毛克利问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“整个村庄。”麦苏雅的丈夫回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们认为我们是富有的巫师，会施巫术。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利被所有关于巫术的话弄糊涂了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巫师到底是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！”麦苏雅对丈夫说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不是巫师。他是我的儿子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是儿子还是巫师，有什么关系？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人回答道，“我们会死的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利指着窗户。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们现在自由了，走吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“往哪儿走？”麦苏雅的眼睛瞪得大大的，显得很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不了解森林，而且我受伤了，我走不太快。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“村民们会跟着我们的。”她丈夫补充道，“没希望了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利听到外面传来高喊声和脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听上去像是布尔迪奥回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>想想你们要去哪里。我马上回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跳出窗户，爬回了树那边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥躺在地上，边咳嗽，边呻吟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人群在大声问他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你杀死那个男孩儿了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他又施巫术了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥咕哝了什么，然后叫人给他拿水来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我先喝一杯水，然后我再给你们讲我的故事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哼！”毛克利对自己说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人类只会说话。他们将永远待在树下！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利回到小屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在他走到窗前的时候， 他感觉到有什么在轻轻触摸他的脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼妈妈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我跟着你进了这个村庄，毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想见见那个照顾你的女人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“村民们打算杀了她！”毛克利迅速解释道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦苏雅必须穿过森林逃跑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会保护她的。”狼妈妈说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她溜回黑暗中，等待毛克利的命令。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦苏雅和她的丈夫决定去下一个村庄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到那里要几个小时。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利帮助他们从窗户逃了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在星光下，森林显得又黑暗又危险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们认识路吗？”他低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>夫妻俩点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。别害怕。我保证森林会保护你们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在走，慢慢走。不用着急。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泪水从她的脸颊流下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦苏雅拥抱毛克利说再见。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们走进了黑暗的森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈悄悄地跟着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，另一个动物出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巴希拉！”毛克利迅速向他解释了情况。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布尔迪奥还在给村民们讲故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他会停下来的，然后人们就会过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当人们发现这个小屋空了，我们该怎么办呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”巴希拉想了一会儿，“我有一个办法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>